description: One of our favorite dommes, Claire Adams, was kind enough to give us a brief demo on the basics of caning, using Cherry Torn as the ever-willing victim. Novices will appreciate the large amount of information she presents in this small package, a tutorial designed to pique your interest and get you started on the sweet path to defiling unblemished flesh. Yes, we cane!
title: Caning 101 with Claire Adams
